            { //Elements page that covers the basic elements. Each element has 2 content: header(with image), and the desc text.
                "titleText": "Elements - Basics",
                "titleCol": [ 255, 255, 255, 255 ],
                "content": [
                    { // Overview
                        "text": "There are 3 elements.\nDifferent weapons and pets can inflict these elements on their targets",
