                    {
                        "text": "Reduces the defense of its bearer.\n\nWhen hitting the bearer, the attacker is healed.\n\nIf the weapon is melee, the heal is increased.",
                        "contentTxtOrigin": "TEXT_MIDDLE",
                        "contentCol": [ 255, 255, 255, 255 ],
                        "contentPos": [ 500, 40 ],
